00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:49,900
fact, entanglement does count as a proto-measurement that destroys interference. But it's actually

397
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:55,580
much deeper that that. According to the math, entanglement and measurement or the exact

398
00:37:55,580 --> 00:38:03,650
same phenomenon, the math is exactly the same, and that is why entanglement destroys interference

399
00:38:03,650 --> 00:38:07,400
because entanglement is measurement. And I have a lot more to say about that later in

400
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:15,140
the talk. So okay, so there's no interference but now what about this last--the idea of

401
00:38:15,140 --> 00:38:20,370
creating the interference using a quantum eraser. So let's take another look at our--I'm

402
00:38:20,370 --> 00:38:26,820
running little short on time so I'm just going to blast through this. This is what the state

403
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:34,520
equation looks like for the quantum eraser after the so-called measurement but before

404
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:38,350
erasure. So you have an upper photon that's horizontally polarized because we've--let's

405
00:38:38,350 --> 00:38:46,550
assume we start with a vertically polarized light going in here and we measure by rotating

406
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:53,510
90 degrees. So we have now the upper photon rotated from vertical to horizontal and the

407
00:38:53,510 --> 00:39:00,140
