00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:06,410
missing which is also shouldn't be too surprising because we filtered--we put this 45-degree--we

419
00:40:06,410 --> 00:40:13,700
put this filter in place. This filter is filtering out half the photons that go through it. If

420
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:18,230
it--if they come in at 45 degrees then half of them come out polarized this way and the

421
00:40:18,230 --> 00:40:26,390
other half get blocked. So it turns out that the other half, the half that didn't get through,

