00:40:58,350 --> 00:41:02,460
interference but it turns out that they're anti-fringes. They're exactly like the bright

428
00:41:02,460 --> 00:41:08,340
spots in the interference fringes for the photons that got filtered out, exactly lined

429
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:14,580
up with the dark spots of the fringes for the photons that were let through. And they

430
00:41:14,580 --> 00:41:19,530
sum together to produce what we perceived when we look at it as non-interference. So

431
00:41:19,530 --> 00:41:23,480
this quantum eraser doesn't actually erase anything and it doesn't produce interference,

432
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:28,560
it just filters out interference that was actually already there all along. And it turns

433
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:32,590
out that we can actually do this in the EPR experiment too. And the way that we--but in

434
00:41:32,590 --> 00:41:36,660
