00:42:00,170 --> 00:42:04,050
channel. And you look at all the up photons and sure enough there's an interference pattern,

441
00:42:04,050 --> 00:42:06,850
and you look at all the down photons and sure enough there's an interference pattern. But

442
00:42:06,850 --> 00:42:13,450
the only way to see that is to take classical information and move it from here to here.

443
00:42:13,450 --> 00:42:19,690
And that is the last nail in the coffin. I was very disappointed when I learned this

