00:49:12,200 --> 00:49:20,490
particles? You end up with a Venn diagram that looks like this and if we assume a two-state

516
00:49:20,490 --> 00:49:27,230
system then the actual numbers come out looking like this. You've got one bit of information

517
00:49:27,230 --> 00:49:31,800
entropy between A and C, one bit between A and B, and you've got this negative, this

