the negative one, cancel out and become a zero, same thing over here, and what we have

526
00:50:27,670 --> 00:50:36,350
is if we ignore this is exactly the same system from an information theoretical point of view

527
00:50:36,350 --> 00:50:42,410
as a coin with a sensor, we have two classical particles that are perfectly correlated with

528
