00:51:06,560 --> 00:51:10,840
we reflect but actually by ignoring the thing that we're measuring, or that we think we're

533
00:51:10,840 --> 00:51:16,450
measuring. As it turns out that this extends to any macroscopic ecosystem. If you add an

