00:53:06,410 --> 00:53:11,970
them. And in principle, that's possible and in practice, obviously, it's not, which is

554
00:53:11,970 --> 00:53:19,520
why classical measurement seems to be irreversible despite the fact that the physics of the universe

555
00:53:19,520 --> 00:53:25,980
say that everything is reversible. So, this has some philosophical implications. I call

